# Remove extra spaces

This formatter should remove extra spaces.

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

Remove extra spaces in normal text.

- Remove extra spaces in list item

Remove extra spaces in [text]{ .attributes }

Remove extra spaces in {_important text_}{ .with key="value" }

Remove extra spaces in inline { % comments % } [and]{ % comments in
inline attributes % .highlight }

Remove extra spaces in

{ % comments % }
> in block attributes
